						               													<description>Motorsport is a deck building game for 1-4 players that captures the frenzy of automotive competition.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;You will compete against your fellow drivers to build the most competitive car, as quickly as possible. The goal is to win Events, such as drag races, car shows, drift competitions, autocrosses, and circuit races. The first player to win enough Events to claim seven Trophy Points wins the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;You play with a personal deck which you will add to and expand as the game progresses. Your deck starts pretty weak, but each card you add to it will make it stronger! You will build your deck the same way you would build a car: by deciding what your goal is and purchasing Mods that support that goal.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The gameplay in Motorsport revolves around four Upgrade Types: Speed, Style, Handling, and Traction. Vehicles have stats for each Type, Mods belong to and support specific Types, and the winner of Events is determined by Vehicle Upgrade Type stats. You can choose which of the four Types you want to focus on, depending on your play style!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
